name: Release 3.4.0
body: - Add ability to move the TabBar (#258)

name: Release 3.3.3
body: - Changed access control from public to open

name: Release 3.2.0
body: Added optional followers parameter to followScrollView. See [README](https://github.com/andreamazz/AMScrollingNavbar#followers)

name: Release 2.1.2
body: Fix handling of the status bar when in-call
Fix issue with Carthage on targets below 8.4

name: Release 1.1
body:
- Improved Autolayout compatibility. (Now recommended)
- Dropped support for older iOS versions.

name: Release 0.7
body: - Added UIViewController's category. The support for the subclassed version will be dropped in future releases.

name: Release 1.0
body:
- Dropped support to the subclass implementation
- Improved iOS6 compatibility
- Added stopFollowingScrollView
- Removed refreshNavbar method
